Napa Valley Train Gets Nod: The California Public Utilities Commission gave its 
unanimous approval to a settlement that will allow the Napa Valley Wine Train 
to start passenger service through the famed wine valley in about three weeks. 
NVWT President Jack McCormack immediately announced that service between Napa 
