<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: MOVIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Daniel Cerone and Claudia Puig, Arts and entertainment reports from The 
Times, national and international news services and the nation's press. 
