MERCENARIES; MILITARY TRAINING; CARTELS; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- 
COLOMBIA; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SOUTH AMERICA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
