belongings to his van. Michael Gauvin, a security guard, informs Margaret 
Polanco that tenants must be gone by 5 p.m., and Patricia Vasquez sits on a 
couch outside her room, wondering where to move her family. LOU MACK / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, 
</P>
