"Challenge for Children" fund-raiser. Jazz center Mark Eaton, below, towers 
over wife Marcie. ; Photo, The man behind the fund-raiser, Lakers star Byron 
Scott, with his wife, Anita, his daughter, Londen, and son, Thomas, at the 
children's benefit at the Newport Beach Marriott hotel. PAMELA MARIN / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
